SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT CASE WHEN CONVERT(VARCHAR(128), SERVERPROPERTY ('productversion')) like '8%' THEN '2000' WHEN CONVERT(VARCHAR(128), SERVERPROPERTY ('productversion')) like '9%' THEN '2005' WHEN CONVERT(VARCHAR(128), SERVERPROPERTY ('productversion')) like '10.0%' THEN '2008' WHEN CONVERT(VARCHAR(128), SERVERPROPERTY ('productversion')) like '10.5%' THEN '2008' WHEN CONVERT(VARCHAR(128), SERVERPROPERTY ('productversion')) like '11%' THEN '2012' WHEN CONVERT(VARCHAR(128), SERVERPROPERTY ('productversion')) like '12%' THEN '2014' WHEN CONVERT(VARCHAR(128), SERVERPROPERTY ('productversion')) like '13%' THEN '2016' WHEN CONVERT(VARCHAR(128), SERVERPROPERTY ('productversion')) like '14%' THEN '2017' WHEN CONVERT(VARCHAR(128), SERVERPROPERTY ('productversion')) like '15%' THEN '2019' ELSE '-1' END AS MajorVersion
